S.FORM: Lou Boudreau, u tatama. pulecuhan ciniza i Harvey, Illinois, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. nalecuhan ciniza i 7 a bulad 17 a demiad, 1917 a mihcaan, Lou Boudreau, miunduay. mapatay i 2001 a mihcaan. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan u piazihan tu sulit nu ayzaay a tabakiay a mikeliday asaca angangan nu kanatal atu sefu(Lists of National Basketball Association players)
